<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A5DFFC2D2AB0F28FE40F967" blockId="3.[211,1444,1601,1863]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">
En dehors des deux femelles types conservées à Paris (MNHN), 
<typeStatus id="5489A8E81A5DFFC2D1D60F28FC7AF9DE" box="[911,1001,1601,1624]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">holotype</typeStatus>
du camp du Zougué (
<date id="FF8C308A1A5DFFC2D68F0F28FAAEF9DE" box="[1238,1341,1601,1624]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" value="1957-01-28">28.I.1957</date>
, Lamotte, Amiet et Vanderplaetsen, 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A5DFFC2D3850F0DFDBDF9FD" box="[476,558,1636,1659]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" unit="m" value="1050.0">1050 m</quantity>
) et 
<typeStatus id="5489A8E81A5DFFC2D00C0F0DFD3DF9FD" box="[597,686,1636,1659]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">paratype</typeStatus>
de Danané (
<date id="FF8C308A1A5DFFC2D1680F0DFCEBF9FD" box="[817,888,1636,1659]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" value="1939-01">I.1939</date>
, L. Chopard), l’espèce est maintenant connue par une troisième femelle en provenance de Lamto (forêt-galerie du Bandama, 
<date id="FF8C308A1A5DFFC2D1E90FEFFC64F91B" box="[944,1015,1670,1693]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" value="1982-01">I.1982</date>
), citée par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A5DFFC2D6320FEFFA33F91B" author="LE GALL P. &amp; MESTRE J." box="[1131,1440,1670,1693]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" pagination="41 - 64" refId="ref42048" refString="LE GALL P. &amp; MESTRE J. 1986. - Les Acridiens (Insecta Orthoptera) de la region de Lamto. Annales de l'Universite d'Abidjan (serie E) 18: 41 - 64." type="journal article" year="1986">Le Gall &amp; Mestre (1986: 45)</bibRefCitation>
. L’holotype est figuré de profil dans la description originale, et un dessin plus détaillé de son extrémité abdominale figure dans 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A5DFFC2D3530FA3FE5DF967" author="MESTRE J." box="[266,462,1738,1761]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" refId="ref42085" refString="MESTRE J. 1988. - Les Acridiens des formations herbeuses d'Afrique de l'Ouest. Ministere de la Cooperation, Paris; CIRAD-GERDAT-PRIFAS, Montpellier, 332 p." type="book" year="1988">Mestre (1988: 39)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32845C11A5DFFC5D2AB0F85FBABFBA9" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="315" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A5DFFC2D2AB0F85FA30F8C1" blockId="3.[211,1444,1601,1863]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A5DFFC2D2AB0F85FE40F885" author="DESCAMPS M." box="[242,467,1772,1795]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" refId="ref40707" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1964. - Revision preliminaire des Euschmidtiinae (Orthoptera: Eumastacidae). Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle 30 (A), Paris: 321 p." type="book" year="1964">Descamps (1964: 65)</bibRefCitation>
a décrit une autre espèce qu’il a rapportée avec doute au même genre (
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A5DFFC2D6FF0F85FAE7F885" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1964" box="[1190,1396,1772,1795]" class="Insecta" family="Euschmidtiidae" genus="Mastachopardia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jagoi">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5DFFC2D6FF0F85FAE7F885" box="[1190,1396,1772,1795]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">Mastachopardia jagoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) sur un unique mâle du 
<collectingCountry id="F32556DA1A5DFFC2D3C50E67FE70F8A3" box="[412,483,1806,1829]" name="Liberia" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">Liberia</collectingCountry>
(N.E. of 
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A5DFFC2D0660E67FDE6F8A3" box="[575,629,1806,1829]" country="Liberia" name="Bomi" pageId="3" pageNumber="314">Bomi</collectingRegion>
Hills, mining area N of Monrovia, 
<date id="FF8C308A1A5DFFC2D1810E67FBDCF8A3" box="[984,1103,1806,1829]" pageId="3" pageNumber="314" value="1923-06-23">23.VI.1923</date>
, N. D. Jago), conservé au NHML, dont il a figuré l’extrémité de l’abdomen, l’angle postérieur des lobes latéraux du pronotum et le complexe phallique. Il n’est
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A5AFFC5D3310A51FB3FFCE3" blockId="4.[360,1221,824,869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D3310A51FE00FCCF" bold="true" box="[360,403,824,841]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">FIG.1</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A5AFFC5D3C70A51FD42FCCF" authority="Descamps" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1964" box="[414,721,824,841]" class="Insecta" family="Euschmidtiidae" genus="Mastachopardia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zougueana">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D3C70A51FDEAFCCF" box="[414,633,824,841]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Mastachopardia zougueana</emphasis>
Descamps
</taxonomicName>
, 
<typeStatus id="5489A8E81A5AFFC5D0810A51FC8EFCCF" box="[728,797,824,841]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">holotype</typeStatus>
femelle, longueur 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A5AFFC5D1ED0A51FC7EFCCF" box="[948,1005,824,841]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" unit="mm" value="22.0">22 mm</quantity>
; d’après 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A5AFFC5D6650A51FB52FCCF" author="DESCAMPS M." box="[1084,1217,824,841]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" refId="ref40707" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1964. - Revision preliminaire des Euschmidtiinae (Orthoptera: Eumastacidae). Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle 30 (A), Paris: 321 p." type="book" year="1964">Descamps, 1964</bibRefCitation>
. 
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D3D80A3DFE3FFCE3" bold="true" box="[385,428,852,869]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">FIG.1</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A5AFFC5D3EE0A3DFD7AFCE3" authority="Descamps" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1964" box="[439,745,852,869]" class="Insecta" family="Euschmidtiidae" genus="Mastachopardia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zougueana">
Mastachopardia zougueana 
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D0C10A3DFD7AFCE3" box="[664,745,852,869]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Descamps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D0B00A3DFB3FFCE3" box="[745,1196,852,869]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">
, 
<typeStatus id="5489A8E81A5AFFC5D0AB0A3DFCA4FCE3" box="[754,823,852,869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">holotype</typeStatus>
female, length 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A5AFFC5D1ED0A3DFC7FFCE3" box="[948,1004,852,869]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" unit="mm" value="22.0">22 mm</quantity>
; after 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A5AFFC5D67B0A3DFB3BFCE3" author="DESCAMPS M." box="[1058,1192,852,869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" refId="ref40707" refString="DESCAMPS M. 1964. - Revision preliminaire des Euschmidtiinae (Orthoptera: Eumastacidae). Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle 30 (A), Paris: 321 p." type="book" year="1964">Descamps, 1964</bibRefCitation>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A5AFFC5D2F40AC7FBABFBA9" blockId="4.[173,1407,942,1071]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">
en fait pas impossible qu’il s’agisse de la même espèce qu’au 
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A5AFFC5D15D0AC7FCDEFC43" box="[772,845,942,965]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Nimba</collectingRegion>
, le dimorphisme sexuel étant important dans ce groupe. La description originale de ce mâle renferme en outre des notes de terrain du récolteur, relatives à la coloration de l’insecte vivant et à son habitat dans un défrichement forestier non loin d’une rivière, avec végétation renaissante de petits arbres, toutes indications utiles pour rechercher 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A5AFFC5D00F0D71FD4DFBA9" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1964" box="[598,734,1048,1071]" class="Insecta" family="Euschmidtiidae" genus="Mastachopardia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zougueana">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A5AFFC5D00F0D71FD4DFBA9" box="[598,734,1048,1071]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">M. zougueana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
au 
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A5AFFC5D15C0D71FCD8FBA9" box="[773,843,1048,1071]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Nimba</collectingRegion>
et préciser sa biologie.
</paragraph>
